<C>__{officer michaels }
<D>__{are you awake, sir?}
<A>__{the guy starts to open his eyes a little. michaels grabs the guy's face and slams it back, knocking him out again. fogell jumps a little.}
<C>__{officer micheals}
<D>__{i'm sorry, mclovin. but i really need this to be a private thing.}
<A>__{officer michaels takes out two cigarettes, and gives one to fogell, who accepts, quivering in fear. michaels lights his, then passes the lighter to fogell.}
<C>__{officer micheals }
<D>__{listen mclovin, you... like... officer slater and myself, don't you?}
<A>__{fogell tries to light his cigarette. it takes a few tries and he starts hacking after the first pull.}
<C>__{fogell}
<P>__{(coughing)}
<D>__{umm, yeah, sure. you guys are great.}
