<D>__{yeah, well, we're also on probation. you see, we've actually trashed two other cars. the first time wasn't our fault, and the second time a bee flew in and i freaked out. point is, we trash another car, without a good reason, we're fucked. know what i'm saying?}
<A>__{fogell continues to painfully suck back on the cigarette.}
